	<td bgcolor="#F7F7F7" width="175" valign="top" nowrap>
	<a name="post202077"></a>
	
	<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>JanSorensen</b></font><br>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">Fighting misinformation</font><br>
