	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I did a lot of (mostly forced) experiments in PoE and LDoN hard lately, though nothing ordered and scientific.<br />
<br />
But there were some points which were very obvious:<br />
- CH aggro is capped, and capped low. I very rarely grab aggro with CHs. Seems to be less than SR aggro<br />
- Crits draw more aggro than non-crits. While i could grab aggro for a few hits with SL normal, i once crited SL early in a fight, and the tank was not able to pull aggro off for the about 10s it took the mob to kill me</font></p>
	
	<p></p>
