	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Random points and things to consider.<br />
<br />
Hate list Decay.  It may be a set number or a percent of total.  It may also be faster for some mobs then others.  I have seen anicdotal evidence of this.<br />
<br />
There may be a hate modifier associated with offensive spells.  Flame lick comes to mind here, pretty large hate for a little spell.<br />
<br />
Supernal Light is the big dog of agro for me.  <br />
<br />
I wonder if you hit for less then max on a heal if the agro changes? IE -- Supernal Remedy lands for 300.<br />
<br />
I wonder if the relative levels of the characters involved would effect the tests.  A level 50 character may have more "level(weakness) agro" the the lvl65 chr.<br />
<br />
If you come up with a standard sort of test I will help collect data.</font></p>
	
